    public class UnquotedCsvReader
extends CsvReader
    Parses a stream of simplified CSV information. This class does not handle quoted entries, so the records cannot contain the delimiter. The records also cannot embed a newline. This class is useful for handling CSVs that do not use CSV quote rules for records. Telenav TXD format files, for example, are built this way. It is similar to and derived from class CsvReader except for the lack of double quote handling.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo), ericg, roberts
